    "name": "Gem Rifts",
    "steam_appid": 1801670,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1801670/extras/41037e553dbd5e9832e0ba4024383163.avif?t=1674650271\" width=616 height=113 /></span><br>Ancient portals have been lying dormant, waiting for daring adventurers to travel between worlds.<br>It took thousands of exotic gems, gathered over centuries, to finally open one of these portals.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1801670/extras/53ca046cbb4f1d0673c5bca342077af3.avif?t=1674650271\" width=616 height=113 /></span><br>Your task is to lead an expedition through the portal and protect it from hostile guardian life forms that will try to destroy it.<br>If the portal collapses you will be stranded and unable to send back the gems so desperately needed to open more portals.<br>When you arrive on the planet you must start harvesting resources to build defenses around the portal.<br>Assignment of roles and deciding what to research will be critical to the success of your mission.<br>Although we require a vast number of gems, you will need them to build towers that burn, freeze, shock or disintegrate your foes.<br>It's important to survive, but bring back as many gems as you can,<br>After repelling the last guardian attack wave, the portal will be secure and you may return home to a hero's welcome!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1801670/extras/f4574e9fb12024b21095ce865b7a5dcb.avif?t=1674650271\" width=616 height=113 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Play co-op (up to 4 players) or solo<br></li><li>Unique defenders and towers<br></li><li>Workers hunt, harvest, build and mine<br></li><li>Build Focal towers to protect the portal<br></li><li>Towers can be combined to form new types of towers<br></li><li>Unlock more buildings, units and items using a Research Tree<br></li><li>Assign roles to workers using sliders<br></li><li>Workers go about their tasks automatically<br></li><li>Attack waves will target the portal<br></li><li>Players can trade resources<br></li><li>Defeated guardians drop gems<br></li><li>Unlock new worlds using gems</li></ul>",
